        <p>
          Passionate frontend developer with experience in building responsive
          and user-friendly web applications using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Experience</h2>

        <div class="job">
          <h3>Frontend Developer</h3>
          <span>ABC Company | 2024 - Present</span>

          <p>
            Developed responsive websites and improved user experience
            using modern frontend technologies.
          </p>
        </div>

